投资者可能想了解该新产品的进展情况。关于<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-developing-its-own-generative-ai-chatbot-to-rival-chatgpt-174507671.html">潜在的人工智能相关项目</a>的讨论也一直在幕后进行。我们将更新这篇文章，其中包含库克在电话会议中分享的任何详细信息。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/apple-services-are-making-more-cash-than-ever-but-revenue-shrank-for-the-third-quarter-in-a -row-205545482.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-services-are-making-more-cash-than-ever-but-revenue-shrank-for-the-third-quarter-in-a-row-205545482.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 019bd3ef-5bdb-4031-8a6a-56f9e3f17ad9</guid><dc:creator>内森·英格拉汉姆</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 03 Aug 2023 20:55:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691096391</ingested><modified> 2023-08-03T21:00:03+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Investment & Company Information]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Finance]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Nathan Ingraham]]></category><media:content height="2559" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-11/df102830-65fe-11ed-adff-28e00f8109ad" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2559" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-11/df102830-65fe-11ed-adff-28e00f8109ad" width="3840"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]