pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/arkansas-passes-social-media-law-requiring-age-verification-230716388.html">要求年龄验证的</a>法律。除此之外，人们长期以来担心其反骚扰政策<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-elevate-black-voices-harassment-verification-201238553.html">并不总是足以</a>保护某些人群。从理论上讲，这样的努力可以消除一些对 Meta 纵容滥用行为的抱怨。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/instagram-fights-dm-spam-with-limits-on-text-and-photos-165013992.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/instagram-fights-dm-spam-with-limits-on-text-and-photos-165013992.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 139530c7-aea7-46e3-b081-b136fdb29765</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 03 Aug 2023 16:50:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691082397</ingested><modified> 2023-08-03T17:06:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="3210" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/5e70e440-2650-11ee-9f3d-eca4e21bccd1" width="4918"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3210" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/5e70e440-2650-11ee-9f3d-eca4e21bccd1" width="4918"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><m